--- Required Packages

|       name       |       description       |
---------------------------------------------
 gcc               |  GNU C compiler
 libc              |  GNU C Library
 make              |  GNU make utility to maintain groups of programs
 autoconf          |  A GNU tool for automatically configuring source code
 automake          |  A GNU tool for automatically creating Makefiles
 binutils          |  A set of programs to assemble and manipulate binary and object files
 pkg-config        |  Package compiler and linker metadata toolkit
 libncurses5       |  shared libraries for terminal handling (legacy version)
 libncurses5-dev   |  transitional package for libncurses-dev
 libncursesw5      |  shared libraries for terminal handling (wide character legacy version)
 libncursesw5-dev  |  transitional package for libncurses-dev
 ncurses-doc       |  developer's guide and documentation for ncurses
---------------------------------------------


--- Make sure charset is set to UTF-8
For correct display characters recommended use UTF-8 charset.


--- Spell
$ autoreconf -iv && ./configure && sudo make install


--- Launch and show your best result
$ typp


--- File Structure
/usr/local/bin/typp
/usr/local/share/typp/
/usr/local/share/typp/eng.typp
/usr/local/share/typp/rus.typp
/usr/local/man/man6/typp.6
